{"type": "article", "id": 16477, "title": "Oasis 可携帐篷", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-23T06:40:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 129, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135542HPYBulOs4keyUbK5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个可携带的帐篷，设计师 Vytautas Puzeras 用可弯的木材做骨架，支撑起拱形的球体。透明的材质可以全景仰望星空，有点像住在水晶球里，非常浪漫。帐篷另配有落地窗帘以保护隐私，目前正在测试中。不过 Oasis 还是需要花费半天的时间搭建，是一个尚需技术改进的设计。<a href=\"http://www.puzero.eu/oaz%C4%97-oasis\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143730qRv0NcYyO234iQKP.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143731ruoiQqcR89VS71pG.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143731YjmfiQtegqIFxUNr.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261437315M4Z0jTBK8I3aehO.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143732XPFLKDfMZcR6pqtV.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}